OL,6,FIf drivers who used motor finance to
OL,7,Fbuy their cars are found to have lost
OL,8,Fout, because of unlawful lending
OL,9,Farrangements, they could be in line
OL,10,Ffor automatic compensation.
OL,12,FThe Financial Conduct Authority says
OL,13,Fit wants to consult on an industry-
OL,14,Fwide redress scheme, which would
OL,15,Fcompensate car buyers if firms are
OL,16,Ffound at fault.
