OL,6,FThe regulator is reviewing the past
OL,7,Fuse of motor finance discretionary
OL,8,Fcommission arrangements, and wants to
OL,9,Festablish whether firms failed to
OL,10,Fcomply with requirements and if
OL,11,Fconsumers lost out.
OL,13,FBetween 2007 and 2021, some car
OL,14,Fdealers received undisclosed
OL,15,Fcommissions from lenders when
OL,16,Fcustomers accepted higher interest
OL,17,Frates on car loans.
