OL,6,FIn October 2024, the Court of Appeal
OL,7,Fruled that such undisclosed
OL,8,Fcommissions were unlawful, with the
OL,9,FSupreme Court scheduled to hear an
OL,10,Fappeal in 2025.
OL,12,FIf the Supreme Court upholds the
OL,13,Fprevious ruling, the FCA will launch a
OL,14,Fscheme which will require banks to
OL,15,Fproactively identify and compensate
OL,16,Faffected customers.
OL,18,FIt means individuals won't need to
OL,19,Fraise a complaint for compensation,
OL,20,Fthey will be paid out an amount
OL,21,Fdictated by the FCA.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
