OL,6,FThe FCA said on Tuesday: "We are
OL,7,Fconfirming that if, taking into
OL,8,Faccount the Supreme Court's decision,
OL,9,Fwe conclude motor finance customers
OL,10,Fhave lost out from widespread failings
OL,11,Fby firms, then it's likely we will
OL,12,Fconsult on an industry-wide redress
OL,13,Fscheme. We previously said it is more
OL,14,Flikely than when we started our review
OL,15,Fthat we will introduce an alternative
OL,16,Fway of dealing with complaints.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
