OL,6,F"Under a redress scheme, firms would
OL,7,Fbe responsible for determining whether
OL,8,Fcustomers have lost out due to the
OL,9,Ffirm's failings. If they have, firms
OL,10,Fwould need to offer appropriate
OL,11,Fcompensation. We would set rules firms
OL,12,Fmust follow and put checks in place to
OL,13,Fmake sure they do."
OL,15,FA redress scheme would be simpler for
OL,16,Fconsumers than bringing a complaint,
OL,17,Fthe regulator said.
