OL,6,FIt added: "We would expect fewer
OL,7,Fconsumers to rely on a claims
OL,8,Fmanagement company, meaning they would
OL,9,Fkeep all of any compensation they
OL,10,Freceive. It would also be more orderly
OL,11,Fand efficient for firms than a
OL,12,Fcomplaint-led approach, contributing
OL,13,Fto a well-functioning market in the
OL,14,Ffuture."
OL,16,FThe regulator said it would confirm
OL,17,Fwithin six weeks of the Supreme
OL,18,FCourt's decision if it is proposing a
OL,19,Fredress scheme and if so how it will
OL,20,Ftake the scheme forward.
