OL,6,FThe Financial Ombudsman Service
OL,7,Frecently said that hire purchase
OL,8,Frelated to motor vehicles was the area
OL,9,Fthat generated the most complaints
OL,10,Fbetween October and December 2024. It
OL,11,Fsaid case numbers had risen due to
OL,12,Fcomplaints about motor finance
OL,13,Fcommission arrangements.
OL,15,FJenny Ross, editor of Which? Money,
OL,16,Fsaid: "While much still rests on the
OL,17,FSupreme Court decision, a redress
OL,18,Fscheme would remove the need for
OL,19,Fconsumers to make a direct complaint
OL,20,Fto providers.
